From: Dmitry Belyavskiy <beldmit@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 15 May 2025 13:43:29 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 50/50] openssh-6.7p1-coverity

---
 auth-krb5.c                   | 2 ++
 gss-genr.c                    | 3 ++-
 krl.c                         | 3 +++
